Based on your question, it sounds like you're using Kentico Xperience 13 with ecommerce, is that right?
If so, you'll probably want to post your question [here on Devnet](http:/https://devnet.kentico.com/questions-answers/ "here on Devnet"), or better yet reach out to [Kentico Support](mailto:support@kentico.com "Kentico Support") if you're having specific issues with the software not working how you expect. This community page is for their newest offering, Xperience by Kentico.
